@F recall.py opus 2026-01-10
Summary:
  What: Retrieve understanding by topic
  Purpose: Single entry point for all memory access
  How: Pattern match → UnifiedMemory → display

Entry:
  CLI: py recall <agent> <pattern>
  Pattern: wildcard (*) or exact topic
  Modes: pattern, semantic, literal

Pattern Match:
  Wildcards: fnmatch style (*, ?, [seq])
  Exact: Try exact first, fall back to semantic
  Normalize: hyphens and underscores equivalent

Semantic Search:
  Method: UnifiedMemory.search()
  Types: sys_understanding (shared) + sys_journal (private)
  Threshold: 0.3 minimum similarity

Literal Search:
  Flag: --literal "text"
  Method: Brute force string search
  Use: When semantic misses exact phrases

Display:
  Fresh only: Stale perspectives hidden (hash mismatch)
  Per creator: Group by agent, show newest
  Format: Topic header + content per agent

Architecture:
  Memory: UnifiedMemory | both private and shared
  Filter: mem_type='sys_understanding' for topics
  Journal: mem_type='sys_journal' for private search

Dependencies:
  UnifiedMemory: filter, search
  Hardware: get_enclave for sealed keys
